column1: #Text=[We have received the annexed, per Electric and International Telegraph Company, as part of our ordinary despatch ; but it is evidently only another version of the Manchester Examiners telegram, commented on in our leading article.
#Text=New York, Oct. 21.—0n tho 19th Longstreet attacked Sheridan during a dense fog, before daylight, turning and driving most of his line in confusion, and capturing 20 guns.
#Text=Sheridan rallied his troops, formed Hue of battle, and defeated tbe Confederates in the afternoou, capturing 50 guns, including those previously taken by the Confederates, and 1,600 prisoners.
#Text=LONDON CORN MARKET* (From Kingsford and Lags Circular.)
#Text=English and foreign wheat nominally as on Monday.
#Text=—The arrivals of grain this week are not large.
#Text=The wheat trade to-day is only slow.
#Text=Still our millers have to give last weeks prices to enable them to supply their wants.
#Text=—At our market there was a good attendance of country buyers, and a decidedly better feeling in wheat.
#Text=Transactions occurred at prices unobtainable last week.
#Text=Barley dull; beans and peas firm ; oats trifle dearer, if these easterly winds continue our supply will off, and they will go dearer.
#Text=—We received a good supply of beasts on offer this day, which met a fair inquiry, at about late quotations.
#Text=Sheep were a good time of year supply, the trade steady without alteration in prices.
#Text=Pat pigs a large supply : demand steady, at lower prices.
#Text=Beef, od. to 7d. per lb.; wether mutton, 7*d. to Bid.; ewes, 7d. to 7£d.; bacon pigs, Bs. to 9s. per score; porkets ditto, 9s. 6d. to 10s.

#Text=—At to-days market there was a moderate attendance of town and country millers aud dealers, and a fair sale was experienced for wheat, spriug qualities bringing Id. to 2d. over tho low sales of Tuesday last, and other kinds the extreme rates of that day.
#Text=Oats were more saleable at full prices, aud oatmeal must be quoted 6d. per load dearer.
#Text=Indian corn met with a fair inquiry, at an advance of 9d. per qr.
#Text=Flour more saleable, and in some instauces rather better prices were made.
